Aaj ke daur me bachche jab bade ho jate hai,
Jab maa Baap Lachaar aur budhe ho jate hai,
Apne hi bachcho ke kandho ke bojh bn jate hai |

Bade pyar se bachcho ko padhaya tha,
Khud bhukhe rah ke Bacho ko khilaya tha,
Paisa kamane ke kabil banaya tha |

Bchcho ke khushi me apni khushi pai thi,
Bacho ke aage apni suvidhaye thukrai thi,


Bade pyar se apne bete ki shadi rachai,
Ghar me ek nai bahurani aayi,
Maa ke mn me khushiya chhai |

Yunhi kuch mahine bite,
Hansi khushi ke sare pal bite|

Maa se jyada bharosa ab Bibi pe ho gaya,
Maa ka kharch ab kuch jyada badh gaya,
Maa ke sath rahna ab mehanga pad gaya |

Maa ko chhod ab sahar jane ki baat chali,
Bibi ke sath khud ki saman bhi bandh li,
Ganw ko chhod ab sahar ki rah li |

Maa baap ab shayad bojh bn gaye,
Unke do waqt ke khane se ye garib bn gaye,
Sayad ab un paiso se inke bn gaye |

Maa to maa hai, Vo ab bhi dua hi deti hai,
Shaam ko darwaje se raste ko dekhti hai,
Uski suni ankhe ab Bs roti hi rahti hai

To kya hua jo kalyug me bachche maa baap ko chhod Gaye,
Bibi ke kahne se ghar se nata tod gaye,
Apne ganw ke galiyo se yun muh mod gaye |

Ye riti naya nahi, hai shadiyon purana,
Treta me Ram ka sita sang Ayodhya chhod jana,
Krishna ka mathura chhod Dwarka basana |

Ye sare bhagwan hi to kah late hain,
Maa baap se pahle yahi to puje jate hain,

Ram aur krishna ki rah hi to apnaye hai,
Bibi ke sang apna naya ghar hi to basaye hai,
Barso se aa rahi parampara ko hi to nibhaye hai |

Kuch hamari bhi to baat sun jao,
Us bhagwan se tum kuch achcha kar jao,
Dil se apne maa baap ki sewa kar jao |

Is umar me unhe aur kya chahiye,
Khane aur sone se jyada kuch nahi chahiye,

